==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Birl
<hw>Birl</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>byrlian</ets>. ⟦root⟧92.]</ety> <def>To pour (beer or wine); to ply
with drink; to drink; to carouse.</def> <mark>[Obs. or Dial.]</mark>
<rj><au>Skelton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

